(41, 13, 6, 43, 8, 24, 24, 'I am Christ', 'Connection of Deception and Belief', 'This connection highlights the theme of belief in Christ as essential for salvation. In Mark, the warning against deception emphasizes the need to recognize the true Christ, while John stresses that belief in Him is crucial to avoid dying in sins.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
