(41, 13, 7, 43, 14, 27, 27, NULL, 'Connection of Peace and Troubled Hearts', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of not being troubled in the face of adversity. Mark 13:7 mentions not being troubled by wars, while John 14:27 encourages peace and reassures against fear.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
